# ============================================================================
# TROUBLESHOOTING
# ============================================================================

# DEVELOPMENT:
# - "Cannot connect to Redis" → Start Redis: redis-server
# - "Cannot connect to Ollama" → Start Ollama: ollama serve
# - "FAISS index not found" → Run: python src/load_all_knowledge_base.py

# PRODUCTION:
# - "Cannot connect to database" → Check RDS security groups
# - "Cannot connect to Redis" → Check ElastiCache security groups
# - "Out of memory" → Increase instance size or reduce batch size
# - "Slow queries" → Add database indexes, increase workers

# ALL:
# - Slow embedding → Use smaller model or enable cache
# - Hallucinated answers → Lower HALLUCINATION_THRESHOLD
# - Too strict answers → Raise CONFIDENCE_THRESHOLD
